Quickstrike:




Quickstrike turned around with a much relieved look on his face. He 
grinned seeing Black Arachnia safe. "Ah ain't seen 'em." he said to 
her. "Ah'd tried lookin' fer Tarantulas, but ain't no sight of 'im. 
Maybes he's still about. Who's at base, 'sides Hellboy an' his 
sidekick?"
